Name: Pamela Barnes.
Graduation Year: 2021.
Description: Pamela Barnes is a dedicated Mechanical Engineering student with a strong passion for innovation and learning. Throughout their academic journey, they have gained experience in mechanical engineering research and practical applications. They aspire to become a journalist uncovering critical social and political issues. Their dedication to excellence and problem-solving skills make them a promising professional in their field..
